<div class="my-4 mx-auto p-4 shadow-md rounded-md max-w-lg bg-white">
    <h1>✂️ Magic Scissors</h1>
    <p>
        Create synthetic datasets for computer vision by
        copy/pasting objects of interest on top of
        background images.
    </p>

    <h2>How It Works</h2>

    <p>Magic Scissors will cut out specified foreground objects and place them in unique locations on top of the specified backgrounds.</p>

    <p>
        To use Magic Scissors, you need:
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://roboflow.com">A Roboflow account</a></li>
        <li>A dataset with foreground images</li>
        <li>A dataset with background images</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Magic Scissors supports object detection and image segmentation datasets.</p>

    <h2>Get Started</h2>

    <form id="apiKeyForm">
    <div class="mt-4 mb-5">
        <div class="block mb-2 font-bold text-sm">Enter <a href="https://app.roboflow.com/settings/api" target="_blank">your Roboflow Private API Key</a> to get started:</div>
        <div><input type="password" id="apiKey" value="{{apiKey}}" name="apiKey" placeholder="e.g. M4G1csC15s0RZ" autofocus class="text-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 rounded-sm py-1 px-2 w-72" /></div>
        <div id="errorMessage" class="hidden mt-2 text-red-500 text-xs font-bold"></div>
    </div>

    <div id="submitButtonContainer">
        <input type="submit" class="btn cyan" value="Continue" />
    </div>
    <div id="loadingContainer" class="hidden">
        <div class="btn bg-gray-200"><i class="far fa-spin fa-spinner -ml-1 mr-1"></i> Continue</div>
    </form>
</div>